distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check gives the defined cluster name and IP.
 Second shown information is the quorum drive and typ.

 In order to run, its needed to copy the hyperv_cluster.ps1 script to the plugin
 folder of the agent.

inventory:
 One check is found if cluster data is existing.


